results.name: Normalized sequence of cumulants formed from moments in a quantum many-body problem at its critical point.
link: Sean A. Irvine, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..100
formula: a(n) = (-4)^n / (2 * Pi) * Integral_{x=-oo..oo} sech(x) * tanh^n(x) * (d^(n-1) / dx^(n-1)) tanh(x) dx. [Corrected and improved by _Sean A. Irvine_, Jul 02 2018]
